Basil Read Climbs to 11-Week High After ‘Multi-Billion Rand’ Contract Win

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-04-06T13:09:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-06/basil-read-climbs-to-11-week-high-after-multi-billion-rand-contract-win.html
Basil Read Holdings Ltd. (BSR)  climbed to
an 11-week high in Johannesburg after the company said its Majwe
joint venture has been awarded a “multi-billion rand” mining
services contract by Debswana Diamond Co. in Botswana.  Shares in Basil Read rose as much as 4.8 percent to 12.41
rand, the highest since Jan. 19, and traded at 12.35 rand as of
3:08 p.m. local time.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  